rows.label: qst702503_msg0003
rows.name:
Your Majesty, that was incredible!
I didn't doubt you for a moment!

rows.label: qst702503_msg0005
rows.name:
Oh, haha...
It was nothing special, really...

rows.label: qst702503_msg0006
rows.name:
You didn't come all the way over here
just to say that, did you?

rows.label: qst702503_msg0008
rows.name:
More trouble! The monsters are coming
in from the opposite side now!

rows.label: qst702503_msg0009
rows.name:
So they did bring in reinforcements...
Just as I thought.

rows.label: qst702503_msg0010
rows.name:
Friends of the ones we just took,
maybe.

rows.label: qst702503_msg0011
rows.name:
It's not the usual sort of monster we
see round here either...

rows.label: qst702503_msg0013
rows.name:
I've got a bad feeling about this...
Still, we'd better head out there!

rows.label: qst702503_msg0014
rows.name:
Noowl, I'll ask you to keep watch again.
If you spot anything, let me know about
it right away!

rows.label: qst702503_msg0015
rows.name:
Yes, Your Majesty!
I won't let you down!
